Class BluetoothEnvironmentVariable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.baseclasses.EnvironmentVariable
      • com.pvsagar.smartlockscreen.applogic_objects.environment_variables.BluetoothEnvironmentVariable

  • public class BluetoothEnvironmentVariable
extends EnvironmentVariable
    Created by aravind on 10/8/14. Class representing a BluetoothEnvironmentVariable. Stores 2 strings: Device name and device address Type is given by EnvironmentVariable.TYPE_BLUETOOTH_DEVICES
